{"tid":2124029,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[24-Jul] 立法會期尾飯民陣營全線潰爛：三項撥款議案反勝為敗，將軍澳政府大樓飯民大規模倒戈護航，35+頓成笑話","createTime":"2020-07-25T05:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T05:54:27.000Z","uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c626af36a595ae190fc816a57d3d27b3fe90ad41","tid":2124029,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"跟住奇怪嘅事發生了，明明響無約束力動議果陣飯民仲可以一票之微險勝建制派，<span class=\"red\">點知去到關鍵時刻，<span class=\"gold\">涂謹申<span class=\"red\">梁耀忠<span class=\"gold\">梁繼昌</span>郭榮鏗</span>陳沛然</span>卻同時缺席投票，結果令飯民以1票之微18比19輸比建制反勝為敗。</span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*n1jAj8ddTdd4hpwITBuD_g.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F1%2An1jAj8ddTdd4hpwITBuD_g.jpeg&h=070b3c28&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後再響7月13日，人事編制小組申請新增一個常額首長級丙級政務官，<span class=\"red\">又因為陳沛然投棄權票，梁耀忠同郭榮鏗缺席投票，飯民以20票對22票反勝為敗，無法阻止撥款通過；</span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*sTl8SJhTO3walLN4rQwxsw.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F1%2AsTl8SJhTO3walLN4rQwxsw.jpeg&h=b9e8adab&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後再響2020年7月14日新界綠化總綱圖撥款議案，<span class=\"red\">因為<span class=\"gold\">梁耀忠<span class=\"red\">梁繼昌<span class=\"gold\">郭家麒<span class=\"red\">郭榮鏗</span>朱凱迪</span>陳淑莊缺席</span>，陳沛然棄權</span>，令飯民以17票反對建制18票贊成反勝為敗──明明上面七條友，只要有任何一個轉投反對票，飯民就可以成功擊敗建制派否決財委會撥款議案。</span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*sTl8SJhTO3walLN4rQwxsw.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F1%2AsTl8SJhTO3walLN4rQwxsw.jpeg&h=b9e8adab&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@henryporterbabe/立法會期尾飯民陣營全線潰爛-三項撥款議案反勝為敗-將軍澳政府大樓飯民大規模倒戈護航-35-頓成笑話-80c8159421e3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40henryporterbabe%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%BE%E9%A3%AF%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E7%87%9F%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E6%BD%B0%E7%88%9B-%E4%B8%89%E9%A0%85%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8D%E5%8B%9D%E7%82%BA%E6%95%97-%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E9%A3%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%80%92%E6%88%88%E8%AD%B7%E8%88%AA-35-%E9%A0%93%E6%88%90%E7%AC%91%E8%A9%B1-80c8159421e3&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHdlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=178ddb77\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@henryporterbabe/立法會期尾飯民陣營全線潰爛-三項撥款議案反勝為敗-將軍澳政府大樓飯民大規模倒戈護航-35-頓成笑話-80c8159421e3</a>"},{"pid":"5462ce67653202817513027aabeafc7336d7bf13","tid":2124029,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}